snippet.title: First On Net Aquaman Review | DC | James Wan | Jason Momoa | Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Avengers 4 Trailer Update - https://goo.gl/yPdjTj

Aquaman is one of the most expected films that is to come. It is to be noted that Marvel has been producing top class films for a while now and that DC is trying hard to match those records and expectations! Will Aquaman break them all? Looks like the pre-release buzz has the potential to pull it off! Watch this video to find out.
